post.description:
Sample request:

    POST /v1/deployments
    {
        "title": "Production Release v2.1.0",
        "type": "STANDARD",
        "metadata": {
            "application": "CustomerPortal",
            "version": "2.1.0"
        }
    }

This endpoint supports idempotency via the Idempotency-Key header.

put.description:
This endpoint requires the If-Match header with the current ETag to prevent lost updates.
Deployments in CLOSED state cannot be updated.

Sample request:

    PUT /v1/deployments/{id}
    If-Match: "abc123"
    {
        "title": "Updated Production Release v2.1.1",
        "metadata": {
            "version": "2.1.1"
        }
    }
